1) Write a program to output different messages when number is:
   a. Greater than 3
   b. Lesser than 3
   c. Or equal to 3
   d. Or when the user input is empty
ANS)
    read -p "Number: " n
    if [ $n -eq 3 ]; then
	    echo "number equal to 3"
    elif [ $n -gt 3 ]; then
	    echo "greater than 3"
    elif [ $n -lt 3]; then 
	    echo "lesser than 3"
    else 
	    echo "empty input"
    fi